<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027 0%, #203a43 50%, #2c5364 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        .login-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            overflow: hidden;
            max-width: 850px;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .login-card {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .login-left {
                padding: 1.5rem !important;
            }
            .login-right {
                padding: 1.5rem !important;
            }
        }
        .login-left {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            flex: 1;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .login-left::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .login-right {
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            color: #2b2b2b;
            flex: 1.2;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        .form-control {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
            background: #f4f6f9;
            border: 1px solid #e1e5eb;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .form-control:focus {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
            border-color: #667eea;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .btn-custom {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 0.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            border: none;
        }
        .btn-custom:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px -10px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6);
        }
        .sso-btn {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 0.6rem;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        .sso-saml { background: #e8f4fd; color: #0078D4; border-color: #e8f4fd; }
        .sso-saml:hover { background: #0078D4; color: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 15px -5px rgba(0, 120, 212, 0.3); }
        .sso-oauth { background: #fff4e5; color: #F25022; border-color: #fff4e5; }
        .sso-oauth:hover { background: #F25022; color: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 15px -5px rgba(242, 80, 34, 0.3); }
        .sso-jwt { background: #f3f0ff; color: #7952B3; border-color: #f3f0ff;}
        .sso-jwt:hover { background: #7952B3; color: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 15px -5px rgba(121, 82, 179, 0.3); }

        .divider {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 1.2rem 0 1rem 0;
            color: #a0aab5;
        }
        .divider::before, .divider::after {
            content: '';
            flex: 1;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e5eb;
        }
        .divider:not(:empty)::before { margin-right: 1em; }
        .divider:not(:empty)::after { margin-left: 1em; }
        
        .badge-soft {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: #fff;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-card">
        <!-- Left Side: Branding -->
        <div class="login-left">
            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-2 display-6" style="letter-spacing: -1px;"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill me-3"></i>IAMERT</h1>
            <p class="fs-6 mb-3 fw-light" style="opacity: 0.9; line-height: 1.5;">
                SAML, OAuth 2.0 ve JWT altyapılarınızı doğrulayabileceğiniz güvenli SSO test merkezi.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-auto">
                <span class="badge badge-soft px-3 py-2 rounded-pill mb-2"><i class="bi bi-person-badge me-2"></i>IAM Engineer Hub</span>
                <p class="mb-0" style="opacity: 0.85; font-size: 0.9rem;">Created by <strong>Ömer Mert Kaya</strong></p>
                <a href="https://omermertkaya.github.io" target="_blank" class="text-white small text-decoration-none border-bottom border-light pb-1" style="opacity: 0.85;">omermertkaya.github.io</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Side: Login Options -->
        <div class="login-right">
            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-1">Giriş Yapın</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3 small">Lokal veya Kurumsal Kimlik (SSO) ile devam edin.</p>

            <% if (locals.message) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-danger bg-danger text-white border-0 shadow-sm rounded-3 py-2 px-3 small d-flex align-items-center mb-3" role="alert">
                    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill fs-5 me-2"></i> <div><%= message %></div>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <% if (locals.defaultUser) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-info border-0 shadow-sm rounded-3 py-2 px-3 mb-3" style="background: #e8f4fd; color: #0078D4;" role="alert">
                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2 small"><i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill me-2"></i>Eğitim Modu Aktif</h6>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                        <div class="small w-100 font-monospace">
                            <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                                <li class="mb-1 text-dark"><strong>Kullanıcı:</strong> <%= defaultUser.username %></li>
                                <li class="text-dark"><strong>Şifre:</strong> <%= defaultUser.password %></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <form action="/login" method="POST" class="mb-2">
                <div class="mb-2">
                    <label for="username" class="form-label fw-semibold small text-muted text-uppercase mb-1" style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Kullanıcı Adı</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" name="username" value="<%= locals.defaultUser ? defaultUser.username : '' %>" required placeholder="Kullanıcı Adı">
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="password" class="form-label fw-semibold small text-muted text-uppercase mb-1" style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Şifre</label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" value="<%= locals.defaultUser ? defaultUser.password : '' %>" required placeholder="••••••••">
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100 btn-custom" style="background: #667eea;">
                    Lokal Giriş Yap <i class="bi bi-arrow-right fw-bold ms-1"></i>
                </button>
            </form>

            <div class="divider small fw-bold text-uppercase" style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Veya SSO Kullanın</div>

            <div class="d-flex flex-column">
                <a href="/login/sso" class="sso-btn sso-saml">
                    <i class="bi bi-diagram-3-fill fs-5"></i> SAML 2.0 ile Giriş
                </a>
                <a href="/login/oauth" class="sso-btn sso-oauth">
                    <i class="bi bi-link-45deg fs-4"></i> OAuth 2.0 ile Giriş
                </a>
                <a href="/login/jwt" class="sso-btn sso-jwt">
                    <i class="bi bi-key-fill fs-5"></i> JWT ile Giriş
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-3 pt-2">
                <a href="/" class="text-muted text-decoration-none fw-semibold"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-1"></i>Ana Sayfa</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>